    Class Description
    AddAdvisorEmptyCoPasswordTest
    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values entered except the password confirmation.
    AddAdvisorEmptyDateTest
    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values entered except the date of hiring.
    AddAdvisorEmptyEmailTest
    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values entered except the e-mail.

    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values entered except name.

    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values but the password and password confirmation do not match.

    AddAdvisorWrongEmailTest
    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values but the e-mail is not filled in correctly.
    AddAdvisorWrongPasswordTest
    System Test that tests the functionality of Add Advisor having all the values but the password is not filled in correctly.
